  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.4.1">
<l>māṟṟaracar maṇimuṭiyun tiṟalun tēcum maṟṟavartaṅ kātalimār kuḻaiyun tantai</l>
<l>kāṟṟaḷaiyu muṭaṉkaḻala vantu tōṉṟik katanākaṅ kāttaḷitta kaṇṇar kaṇṭīr</l>
<l>nūṟṟitaḻko ḷaravintam nuḻainta paḷḷat tiḷaṅkamukiṉ mutupāḷai pakuvāy naṇṭiṉ</l>
<l>cēṟṟaḷaiyil veṇmuttañ cintu nāṅkūrt tirutteṟṟi yampalatteṉ ceṅkaṇ mālē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Kaṇṇaṉ who took care of the maddened elephant, protecting [it],</l>
<l rend="indent">appearing [incarnate], arriving</l>
<l>So that the jeweled crowns, courage, and glory of enemy kings,</l>
<l rend="indent">the ear studs of their wives, and his father’s leg fetters together</l>
<l rend="indent">slipped away, you see,</l>
<l>Is my bright-eyed Māl in Tirutteṟṟiyampalam in Nāṅkūr</l>
<l rend="indent">where white pearl[-like buds] from matured bracts of a young areca</l>
<l>Spill into the mud holes of wide-mouthed crabs in ditches</l>
<l rend="indent">which are choked with lotuses with one-hundred petals.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
